{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer-insights", "channel": "customer-data", "user": "samantha.kim", "message": "I've uploaded the latest customer satisfaction survey results to the shared drive. Please take a look and let me know if you have any questions or concerns.", "create_at": 1685748000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales-team", "channel": "customer-handovers", "user": "david.park", "message": "I've completed the handover for the new customer account. All details have been updated in the CRM. Let me know if you need any further assistance.", "create_at": 1685764800000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales-team", "channel": "sales-strategy", "user": "michael.lee", "message": "We've received confirmation that our new store location will be opening on schedule. I'll be sending out a separate email with details on the launch event and promotions.", "create_at": 1685781600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer-insights", "channel": "customer-data", "user": "samantha.kim", "message": "Just a heads up that our data analytics tool will be undergoing maintenance this weekend. Please plan accordingly and let me know if you have any urgent requests.", "create_at": 1685798400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales-team", "channel": "sales-strategy", "user": "michael.lee", "message": "Hey team, I wanted to follow up on our previous discussion about personalization strategies. As you know, having a robust customer data collection is key to making this work. @samantha.kim, can you give us an update on our customer data collection rate as of Q2 2024?", "create_at": 1688246400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales-team", "channel": "sales-strategy", "user": "samantha.kim", "message": "Hi @michael.lee, as of Q2 2024, we've managed to link about 85% of our transactions to customer loyalty accounts. This is a significant improvement from last quarter, and it gives us a solid foundation for implementing personalized marketing campaigns and improving customer engagement.", "create_at": 1688246460000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales-team", "channel": "sales-strategy", "user": "david.park", "message": "That's great to hear, @samantha.kim! With that level of data collection, we can start creating more targeted promotions and offers. @michael.lee, should we start brainstorming some ideas for personalized campaigns to roll out in Q3?", "create_at": 1688246520000}}
